name: Demon Slayer (New shirt for 2013!)
description: Black ink on a heather gray shirt. A small run, but we made most sizes. Get battle ready with this awesome skull design. See you in the pit, warriors!

name: The Stella Shirt
description: Black cotton tee with bright blue ink. Stella is the girl of your wildest dreams. Full of exhaust pipes, stitches, drool and band aids. Comes in most sizes. Subject to what is left. Get her before she's gone.

name: Scott Aicher.com Trading Cards!
description: People always want to see my black line ink work. It's what I am known for. So I decided this was a good way to get a nice collection of my work. Many of these started out as desk doodles at work presented here in stunning black and white as the art was made. Very limited run. On sale the first month (January 2013) for just 10 Dollars a set. Each 36 card set comes in it's own plastic protective case with an authenticity stamped,signed, and numbered card. All put together one set at a time by the artist himself. In stock,on sale, and ready to ship to you now. What a great way to kick start your new year inspiration!

name: The Aicher Funpack! (Stickers, buttons etc...)
description: In the funpack you will get buttons from local san pedro bands and Scott Aicher stickers! (I will give you a bunch of the different designs I have). You may get an old original flyer! (wow, some of my flyers are rare!). I may send you a comic book I made. You will get lots of stuff for just a few bucks. That's why it called the funpack, Capeesh?
